        <abstract>
            <p>Grateful for addresses of informants, especially that of Rajah James Brooke.</p> 
<p>Dispatch of queries on expression. Answers will make interesting appendix to his "Essay on man" [<hi rend="italic">Descent</hi>].</p> 
            <p>Protective adaptation of female butterflies believed probable.</p>
            <p>Believes in sexual selection as applied to man.</p>
        </abstract>
